    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Tear your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>into bite-sized pieces and add to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 6-7 min or until golden and crisp, then leave to cool \u2013 these are your <strong>crispy ciabatta croutons</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p><p>Dice your <strong>cucumber </strong>finely</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>diced cucumber</strong> and <strong>sliced shallot</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>traditional Italian</strong> <strong>pesto </strong>(you'll use the rest later!),<strong> </strong>1 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 1/4 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [3 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of<strong> sugar </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong>, and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside \u2013 this is your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and tear into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining pesto</strong> to a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>pesto dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained beans</strong>,<strong> torn lettuce</strong> and <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> to the tomato salad</p><p>Gently stir it all together \u2013 this is your <strong>white bean caprese salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/white-bean-and-tomato-caprese-salad-with-pesto-dressing/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> white bean caprese salad </strong>topped with the <strong>crispy ciabatta croutons</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>pesto dressing</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
